Argentina Beats Scotland 13-12 in Rugby World Cup Pool B Game

-- B y   D a n   B a y n e s
-- 
2011-09-25T09:19:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-25/argentina-beats-scotland-13-12-in-rugby-world-cup-pool-b-game.html
Argentina  beat Scotland 13-12 in a
Rugby World Cup Pool B match in Wellington,  New Zealand .  Lucas Gonzalez Amorosino scored the only try of the game
with seven minutes remaining to get Argentina to within a point
and Felipe Contepomi converted to give his team the lead.  Ireland earlier routed Russia 62-12 to regain the Pool C
lead from  Australia , while Samoa beat Fiji 27-7 to stay in
contention of winning Pool D.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Baynes at 
 dbaynes@bloomberg.net  